---
title: Beef & Pork Sausage Rolls with Potato Wedges, Onion Chutney & Cucumber Salad
description: It’s been an age-old battle between the pie and the sausage roll, but this beef and pork sausage roll might be taking home the
crown. A mixed sesame seed pastry holds it all together and goes great with an onion chutney for dipping. Serve with a side of
golden potato wedges and this dinner will rise to the top as the number one sausage roll.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-pork-sausage-rolls-891a6497.jpg
